{"tid":1193407,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班達衛兵知唔知咩叫紅衛兵？仲敢叫人做連衛兵","createTime":"2019-06-09T01:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T03:04:03.000Z","uid":71389,"like":15,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d01ff45c987352c56b4320037be0145c8b878af","tid":1193407,"uid":71389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:49:19.000Z","msg":"最早的紅衛兵名稱來自於一位清華附中學生張承志的筆名（根據駱小海與宋柏林的回憶，張承志最早的筆名是「紅衛士」），意為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保衛毛主席</strong></span>的紅色衛兵」。<br />\n<br />\n紅衛兵在領取毛澤東的旨意後，奔赴全國各地。他們<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>忠心不貳</strong></span>，對毛澤東的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">崇拜狂熱到宗教信仰的境界</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔而家祟拜緊連仔？保衛緊邊個？講解嚟聽下？<br />\n而家港難當前，仲講唔表態就係一種言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似唔似保衛緊一個崇拜偶像而扭曲自己思維嘅人？<br />\n<br />\n呢班連登仔起碼用緊自己批判思維去作出抨擊<br />\n你班達衛兵就真係由頭到尾保衛緊你嘅偶像喇<br />\n根本無自己批判思維，純粹為咗維護自己偶像<br />\n<br />\n仲笑人連衛兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=0a5be0b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc24daccba429f69be872a7de1c1cc56ce96ef2e","tid":1193407,"uid":71389,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:50:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10ad6ea9f7a5912566cf53e34192ea36c444f91","tid":1193407,"uid":32577,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾梗係撐垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67df407dd50dd3460dbb146c18dd2746115f57c","tid":1193407,"uid":71389,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d10ad6ea9f7a5912566cf53e34192ea36c444f91","tid":1193407,"uid":32577,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾梗係撐垃圾<img sr